“And, when you want something, all the universe conspires in helping you to achieve it.” — @paulocoelho, The Alchemist ⁣

Today, I was blessed to sit down with two of the most prolific figures in basketball. Shout out to my guys @_stak5_ and @matt_barnes9. We talked life, passions, the past and present state of sports and hip-hop, and what fuses them all together. Be sure to check me out on @allthesmoke! Details coming soon. #allthesmoke #showtime

I had a great time catching up with @josephsikora4 at his “Fear” movie premiere last night. He gave me a wonderful reminder, in person and through his movie character, that anything in life is within reach, and the power of manifestation is real. :: Please check out “Fear.” Coming to theaters on 01.27.2023. You’ll be blown away by @josephsikora4’s acting versatility!

✨Everything feels better with you by my side.✨⁣⁣
⁣
Happy birthday, David Mays!⁣⁣ 💙
⁣⁣⁣
It’s hard to believe we’ve celebrated seven birthdays together. But it’s harder to imagine life without you next to me. Though we’re always side by side, you lead me in more ways than you’ll ever know, and I’m forever grateful for all that you’ve shown me and taught me. I love you! 637.
Love Languages. 🌹

Ill be in #SaltLake for @nba All-Star Weekend 🙌⭐️ THIS Sunday (3.19) co-hosting the @let_our_vision_evolve Legendary Uno tournament & day party with Hall Of Famer @gary.payton.20! There will also be a LIVE recording of @trashhtalkshow hosted by @bubbadub94 with special guests. See y’all in Utah!

Please help me wish a very happy birthday to the most important, most beautiful and most special person in my life @igobybrettj 🥰❤️🥳 Baby I love you soooooo much I’m so blessed to have you in my life and always by my side 🙏

I had a great conversation with two @nba champions who have been killing the sports & podcast game for a while now with their @allthesmoke show. I have to say thank you to @_stak5_ and @matt_barnes9 for having me on their platform. I hope y’all enjoy the interview it’s out now on the @shobasketball YouTube channel check it out! #HipHop #Sports #TheCulture #AuthenticVoices #BreakbeatMedia #TheSource #TheSourceAwards #TheCreator #GodfatherOfHipHopMedia
Ain’t no woman like the one I got. #wce #wcw

Thank you to @madeinthedmv for having me at #MadeCon this weekend! Got a chance to meet one of DC’s rising stars @fat_gleesh_ and chop it with my man the DC legend @curtbone_dc along with a lot of other great folks. There was a wealth of valuable information being shared.

My guy @nelly once said I had a “little jump” on me 🏀 (see photo caption) when I was featured in #Details magazine. Catch me in the gym now — I guarantee you, my “little jump” is much bigger and better after hitting the bag 🥊 #throwback #fbf

For two years, I watched this amazing woman sweat, cry, stress and jump for joy (literally) with every A. She even brought a professor to tears (TWICE) with her words in a paper and speech. Needless to say, she earned this masters degree. And today, I witnessed her graduate summa cum laude from one of the top universities in the world. I’m humbled. #luckyme 💟

You are my love. My sweetheart. My everything. At 6:37 pm on 06.28.2023, we started the rest of our lives together when you said, “Yes!” (Well, you actually said “absolutely.” Lol.)

I love you, Brett Joléy Jeffries and I can’t wait for you to be my wife.

🚨 NEW PODCAST ALERT 🚨 Breakbeat Media presents Collect Call with Suge Knight 📞 We are bringing you raw and unfiltered conversations between the incarcerated legendary founder of Death Row Records and some of hip-hop culture’s most influential figures - past, present and future.
